{"tid":138183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【生物打印機】3D打印皮膚技術大突破，望助燒傷者重獲新生","createTime":"2017-02-28T11:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T13:36:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"186f6d207b893d0b1dc126402c3cd20bef43d94e","tid":138183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/bioimpresora_uc3m_6-720x480-c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fbioimpresora_uc3m_6-720x480-c.jpg&h=6d6fb1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西班牙研究團隊近日宣佈成功打造一部生物打印機，利用「生物墨水」打印出仿人類皮膚，可以用作醫學人工植皮或研究用途。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by Digital Trends<br />\n<br />\n3D打印皮膚技術透過連接計算機，精確有序地複制自然皮膚的結構，即由血漿、蛋白質及皮膚細胞等組成的「生物墨水」，從外到內「打印」出超仿真人類皮膚：外部第一層的表皮（epidermis）肩負著保護防禦的重任；而內部較厚的一層真皮（dermis），則由成纖維細胞所組成，能夠產生膠原，為皮膚提供彈性及抵抗身體活動時所產生的阻力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by Digital Trends<br />\n<br />\n研究人員指出，最關鍵是掌握「生物墨水」中的成份比例，研究如何才能有效混合各種結構材料，以及如何避免在打印過程中破壞皮膚細胞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by Digital Trends<br />\n<br />\n目前這項技術仍處於實驗階段，現正等候相關部門審批。若能成事的話，生物打印機將能打印出仿人類皮膚。除了大約兩星期的皮膚培養過程外，只須一至兩天的時間便能打印出人造皮膚，為燒傷者或嚴重皮膚患者提供醫學植皮。"},{"pid":"665e8dd6edcc8edb3769c9d8af4d2e1fd0d1e293","tid":138183,"uid":14442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:44:36.000Z","msg":"輕薄的假像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a093e61516630f6fdc289c6e1366c8e82cd182a","tid":138183,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:54:22.000Z","msg":"不久將來3D打印條女出黎砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5a166b585c232516330ee3172e0fdb4ab748c8","tid":138183,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:02:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不久將來3D打印條女出黎砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌屌下突然對手捉撚實你，之後開眼望住係咁大笑，再黎對眼開始變紅，然後就......"},{"pid":"752c60d9982f0e6eb6beb8d6b8b7f593a40850e8","tid":138183,"uid":45840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"打你老母造"},{"pid":"cc5cd54deded39cc99e51833fb04244e0b0c2d83","tid":138183,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不久將來3D打印條女出黎砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌屌下突然對手捉撚實你，之後開眼望<span style=\"color: red;\">你</span>係咁大笑，再黎對眼開始變紅，然後就......</blockquote>"},{"pid":"47df3ba3bb4cc698bdc4d0ae53a7b9e72fea9791","tid":138183,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不久將來3D打印條女出黎砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌屌下突然對手捉撚實你，之後開眼望<span style=\"color: red;\">住你</span>係咁大笑，再黎對眼開始變紅，然後就......</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"601ece2f22d86eeb0e9e851e5338362ff0006ed1","tid":138183,"uid":3698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"人皮假面<br />\n職業特工隊"},{"pid":"629a6092660a2240e6bc6f39d236a629e24429c7","tid":138183,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:10:20.000Z","msg":"耶撚又可以出黎發表下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57453ae415f41b572ce77b77c7bf16ca294230e8","tid":138183,"uid":17768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"Westworld ?"},{"pid":"2317f53c73439530000363659fa49be186d8bcbc","tid":138183,"uid":59